    <entry name="AstraMilitarum/HoldTheLine" value="Hold the Line"/>
    <entry name="AstraMilitarum/HoldTheLineDescription" value="Grants bonuses to allied infantry. Radius is increased upon levelling up this ability. <string name='Traits/HoldTheLineDescription'/>"/>
    <entry name="AstraMilitarum/HoldTheLineFlavor" value="&quot;Side by side with the Astra Militarum, the entire Valhallan people is rising in defence of our native land!&quot;"/>
    <entry name="AstraMilitarum/ThePeoplesCommissar" value="The People's Commissar"/>
    <entry name="AstraMilitarum/ThePeoplesCommissarDescription" value="Grants buffs and instant healing to allied infantry. Duration is increased upon levelling up this ability. <string name='Traits/ThePeoplesCommissarDescription'/>"/>
    <entry name="AstraMilitarum/ThePeoplesCommissarFlavor" value="Typically, Valhallan senior leadership enforce discipline by the point of many bolt pistols. The most experienced among them know when it's better to catch flies with honey; allowing their men to have more luxurious rations can, at times, motivate them better than any threats. Good Marshals know too much honey will fatten the men beyond usefulness; bad ones don't live long enough to internalise this lesson. Gifts must be held by a strong hand, and the men must not forget who is feeding them."/>
